Directory: src/core/router
Purpose: Houses routing algorithms and custom cost functions.
Responsibility: Calculates the shortest path between two coordinates using Dijkstra or A*. Allows injecting customizable CostFunctions to adjust travel times based on turn angles, traffic lights, and surface conditions.
Key Files:
- router.ts: Dijkstra algorithm implementations of the IRouter interface.
- cost.ts: Pre-defined cost weighting formulas (e.g., stopping avoidance vs. speed).
